Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:12.46,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな未来も　ふたりで見たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:19.01,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな想いも　伝わる距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:25.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}君の旅立ち　覚悟してたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:31.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}背中押す言葉　声にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.65,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}最後につよく　抱きしめたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:44.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}ぬくもりと同じだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:52.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀しみが　僕の心つつんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:58.26,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}優しくなるための　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:04.93,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕だけの幸せをくれたひと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.52,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつかまた会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:13.31,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本当の君が見つかるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:19.03,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑顔忘れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:12.46,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論何種未來 都想一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:19.01,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你伴我身畔 思緒才能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:25.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}早已有所準備 你會踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:31.90,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}幾欲衝口而出 終究未能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.65,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}直至分別之際 深深擁抱過後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:44.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}與溫暖同等份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:52.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀傷將我的心包覆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:58.26,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}為了變得溫柔 就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:04.93,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}令我獨佔幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.52,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至再會之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:13.31,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至覓得真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:19.03,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}莫要忘記笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 過去的店長？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花的數量少了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從路前面的市民會館搬去北町
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花束的定期訂貨量就減少了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明那麼喜歡做花束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買 來做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基調… 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用大花好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有什麼推薦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個鬱金香的新品種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多少錢的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5000日元左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般會拿出丈夫的襯衫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是舊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件襯衫我可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣機正在高速運轉中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就乾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的遺物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明讓她扔掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨蛋… 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲帶怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好隨便的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望由你選
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在同樣的距離上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭話時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到你的回應…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能再次像這樣送你花束…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好… 可愛過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位旅途中人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有見到王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長 你這是拇指公主的cosplay嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拇指公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從鬱金香裡誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是從什麼花裡誕生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這妖精式的發言算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意陪我一起找王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還完全不瞭解這裡的世界觀耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然對幽靈說了糊塗話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為… 為什麼要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成兔子眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是進去東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要揉比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是隱形眼鏡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君視力不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如摘下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎麼摘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在我和太太感動的再會中潑涼水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君的眼珠子！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼珠會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家明明有尖端恐懼症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「人家」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 去洗手間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全醉掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣仔細看來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君好年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚光滑的過分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好健康
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈你的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不帶這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠處一片模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把隱形眼鏡摘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但居然會這樣模糊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘下來的隱形眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 兩枚都是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軟趴趴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經廢掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我住一夜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不認識葉月家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視野模模糊糊的 一步也不想走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就睡在店裡 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隱形眼鏡什麼的… 讓我怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡是怎麼做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喝了多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微躺一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你要留宿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道這傢伙趁著酒興會做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要問我怎麼辦… 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會化成這樣出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣稱呼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 這個稱呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是老姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你住下了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個是怎麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那副眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是這個意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 明明想要副最土的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便宜貨卻都很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君的錢包癟掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開盆栽店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在我們店買的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在肩頭上的公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛過頭了讓我有點困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說探病送盆栽不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那說法能改改嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話可不像花店的人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說會在病房扎根 完全是迷信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這間病房陽光這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去我這樣住院時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會寫絲瓜觀察日記當作業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但老爸說會生根 阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得朋友來探病時 給我帶來了種子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,種在土裡已經是兩年以後了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家捧著沉甸甸的綠色四角花盆回去的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是運動會還是郊遊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被我錯過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄成了我的特技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可奈何之事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無處宣洩的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不能隨便深埋入心底的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經埋掉的堅硬種子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被忘卻之時會生根發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬱金香在畫書或孩子的塗鴉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明被畫的很低調
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但實際開花時 卻又大又有魄力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能和種類有關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是打工青年的葉月啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的形象變化好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留這麼長瀏海 所以視力才會下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說我遜斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好遜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是自己剪的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錢沒頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是除了年輕一無所有的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 剪得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮在眼前晃 確實很煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄巧成拙了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說我也曾在眼前晃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看過葉月君的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堅強而靦腆的貧窮青年的輪廓浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是陳腐的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是不合時宜的亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮還會長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被幽靈同情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會… 無限的長出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡剛才也走過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個謎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丈夫什麼時候才能過癮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 是個謎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才一直在走 為什麼不會累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是一團謎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說最大的謎團就是這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不到王子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這一頁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頁？ 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在其他頁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼頁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變大以後更有cosplay的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閒著不知怎樣打發時間的小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把佩劍換成了彩色鉛筆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把盾牌換成了寫生簿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在醫院旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有條長長的林蔭道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同級生每天經過那裡的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能從樹葉的間隙裡看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法叫住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能遙望著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因為不想被家人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為苦肉計
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便有了這篇樹蔭觀察日記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春夏秋冬 這條林蔭道表情轉變好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愉悅了王子的視線 安慰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫生簿越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了那個數量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被送去廢紙回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現的太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平時只會滿嘴風涼話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是緊緊握著絲瓜種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把人生倒著數
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全心全意生存著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越不認輸的人越喜歡裝無所謂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我就是喜歡他這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕不是你認識的店長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是來誘拐我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要扔下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 燕子受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未完的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再詳細點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫到一半的畫書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大成人的王子毫不吸取教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又把好多東西鎖在了紙上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午飯吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 炒飯套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃了 隨便對付的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨應該不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工錢能提前給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午飯也沒吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要讓葉月君吃六花做的菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好恨葉月君肚裡的饞蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直沒吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的餐桌 我記得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面有人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在視野一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君的餐具在動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貪吃鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說我想盡量吃點好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 就是貪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和誰在哪裡吃比較重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿嘴這種話的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後沒法從嘴吸收營養了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神也真是壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人用島尾君的餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我又喜 又悲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同咀嚼食物 嚥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在肚子正中暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從島尾君那裡得到了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間不長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫的病情比較穩定的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們經常兩人去爬山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是踩著腐葉土向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就幸福得很
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到葉月君吃得這麼香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我在浴室裡幫你擦背嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:32.34,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}いつも夢のなかでは　あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:39.55,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}どうして　ねえ　消えないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.64,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}I gave you everything. You gave me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.31,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}きっと　いつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.23,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}You're everything, still my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.44,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}愛しているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:22:05.87,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}真夏に降った雪のような　それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:16.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会わなければ　こんなに切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:23.85,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}胸を締め付けることもなかった　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:36.19,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会えなければ　強さも優しさも　知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:45.41,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}目を閉じれば　すぐそこに　あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:32.34,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}在夢中 你總帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:39.55,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}為什麼 揮之不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.64,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我給了你全部 你給了我何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.31,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}我堅信 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:50.23,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}你是我的全部 仍是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.44,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我都深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:22:05.87,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}彷如夏日飛雪 那是如夢似幻的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:16.17,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不會如此五味雜陳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:23.85,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}不會心如刀絞 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:36.19,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不知何謂堅強與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:45.41,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}合上眼簾 近在咫尺 有你相伴
